					<![CDATA[
						 <p>When the description mentioned the dissolution frequency, my first thought was of '80s hair-metal and &quot;panty melting&quot; guitar solos. Which made the origin story in the final addendum doubly amusing.</p> <p>One pedantic question: Why didn't The Foundation go with &quot;Plan B&quot; containment from the start? It seems like a much more efficient use of resources and manpower to sow a cover story and then let the FDA (or whatever the relevant agency would be) handle it from there.</p> 
				 	]]>
