					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-643231#post-1751174</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-643231/scp-1755#post-1751174</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2013 18:12:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Anaxagoras</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1019930</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, they themselves aren't terribly anomalous. Nothing the worms do is remotely magical. But they shouldn't exist in the first place. They're an engineered organism of sufficient complexity that we don't have anywhere near the skill in synthetic biology to produce, even in 2015.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-643231#post-1751167</guid>
